{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-040","title":"Sentence 40","sectionId":"sentences-031","sectionTitle":"Sentence 31-40","pageStart":270,"pageEnd":276,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":40,"duplicateEntryCount":7,"pages":[{"number":270,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 40"},{"type":"text","text":"Acids are chemical compounds that, in water solution, have a sharp"},{"type":"text","text":"taste, a corrosive action on metals, and the ability to turn certain blue"},{"type":"text","text":"vegetable dyes red."},{"type":"text","text":"酸是一种化合物，在溶于水时，它具有强烈的气味，对金属有"},{"type":"text","text":"腐蚀作用，并且能够使某些蓝色植物染料变红。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"本句的主干是Acids are chemical compounds。其后的that引导一个"},{"type":"text","text":"定语从句修饰compounds。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"acid /ˈæsɪd/ n. 酸，酸性物质","headword":"acid"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 acid rain 酸雨"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 acidic a. 酸性的"},{"type":"text","text":"acidity n. 酸性"},{"type":"entry","text":"compound /ˈkɑːmpaʊnd/ n. 化合物，混合物","headword":"compound"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 com（共同）+pound（放置）→放到一起使合成→化合物"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 chemical compound 化合物"},{"type":"text","text":"compound eye 复眼"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 mixture n. 混合物"},{"type":"entry","text":"solution /səˈluːʃn/ n. 溶液；解决（办法）","headword":"solution"}]},{"number":271,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"记忆 solu（溶解）+tion→让其充分溶解→溶液"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 water solution水溶液"},{"type":"text","text":"saline solution盐溶液"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 liquor n. 溶液"},{"type":"entry","text":"sharp /ʃɑːrp/ a. 强烈的；锋利的；敏锐的","headword":"sharp"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 sharp mind敏锐的头脑"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 sharply ad. 急剧地"},{"type":"text","text":"sharpen v. 削尖"},{"type":"entry","text":"corrosive /kəˈroʊsɪv/ a. 腐蚀（性）的","headword":"corrosive"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 corrosive effect 腐蚀性作用"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 corrode v. 侵蚀，腐蚀"},{"type":"text","text":"co