ium"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 sodium chloride 氯化钠"},{"type":"entry","text":"sulfur /ˈsʌlfər/ n. 硫","headword":"sulfur"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 sulfuric acid 硫酸"},{"type":"text","text":"与化学反应相关的词："},{"type":"entry","text":"artificial /ˌɑːrtɪˈfɪʃl/ a. 人造的","headword":"artificial"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 artificial fertilizer 人工肥料"},{"type":"entry","text":"catalyst /ˈkætəlɪst/ n. 催化剂","headword":"catalyst"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 cata（在…下面）+lyst（分开）→在下面起分解作用→催化"},{"type":"text","text":"剂"},{"type":"entry","text":"dissolve /dɪˈzɑːlv/ v. 溶解","headword":"dissolve"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 dis（分离）+solv（松开）+e→分散→（使）溶解"},{"type":"entry","text":"refine /rɪˈfaɪn/ vt. 提炼，精炼","headword":"refine"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 re（一再）+fine（好的）→使变好→精炼"},{"type":"entry","text":"solvent /ˈsɑːlvənt/ n. 溶剂","headword":"solvent"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 solv（=solu解开；溶解）+ent→溶剂"},{"type":"entry","text":"synthetic /sɪnˈθetɪk/ a. 合成的","headword":"synthetic"}]},{"number":276,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"搭配 synthetic dye 合成染料"}]}]}